               <msContents>
                  <summary>Acts of Täklä Haymanot; Eighteen Miracles of Täklä Haymanot; Concluding Prayer</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Codex">
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>
                           
                           <material key="parchment"/>
                        </support>
                        <extent>
                           <measure unit="leaf">240</measure>
                           
                        </extent>
                        <collation>
                          <note>Due to how this codex was digitized, the complications of this quire map cannot be resolved.</note>
                        </collation>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                       <layout columns="2" writtenLines="11"/>
                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                  <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                  <seg type="rubrication">
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተክለ ሃይማኖት</foreign>
                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word Täklä Haymanot is rubricated</desc>
                  </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#1r" facs="001">Fol. 1r</locus><desc>crude drawing of a figure</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#201v" facs="401">Fol. 201v</locus><desc>crude drawing of a figure and a face</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d3">
                    Decorative designs:
                    <locus target="#4r #71v #97r" facs="006 141 192">folss. 4r, 71v, 97r, </locus> (line of red dots);
                    <locus target="#74r #147r #153r #157v #160r #201r #239r #240v" facs="146 292 304 313 318 400 476 479">74r, 147r, 153r, 157v, 160r, 201r, 239r, 240v</locus> (line of alternating red and black dots);
                    multiple full stops used as section dividers used throughout
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    Measurements for this manuscript were not taken at the time of digitization
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#112v #164v #114v #230r #232r" facs="223 237 227 258 462">Fols. 112v, 164v, 114v, 230r, 232r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Due to the failure to take pictures of the entire folio (showing both gutter and fore edge), it has been impossible to confirm the recto and versoside of many of the folios. There are missing shots between 112v and 164v (possibly 114v) and between 230r and 232r. The previous numbers were allowed to stand, since we cnnot know for sure where the missed shot was
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <desc>
                    Numbered quires: quires 2, 17, 18, 20 and 22
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus target="#7r #8r #15v #18r #21r" facs="012 014 029 034 040">Fols. 7r, 8r, 15v, 18r, 21r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) words of text are written interlinearly;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#40r #182v #192v" facs="078 363 383">Fols. 40r, 182v, 192v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    erasure markings are visible;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <locus target="#23r #46v #55v #57v" facs="044 091 108 113">Fols. 23r, 46v, 55v, 57v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) text has been removed
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </additions>
